---

import FeatImage01 from '../images/features-03-image-01.png';
import FeatImage02 from '../images/features-03-image-02.png';
import FeatImage03 from '../images/features-03-image-03.png';
import FeatImage04 from '../images/features-04-image-04.png';
---

<section>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="border-t border-gray-800 py-12 md:py-20">
      <!-- Section header -->
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl pb-12 text-center md:pb-16">
        <div class="group relative mb-8 inline-flex">
          <div class="absolute -inset-px rounded-xl bg-gradient-to-r from-[#44BCFF] via-[#FF44EC] to-[#FF675E] opacity-70 blur-lg transition-all duration-1000 group-hover:-inset-1 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:duration-200"></div>
          <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full bg-gray-800 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-200">
            探索AI的无限可能
          </span>
        </div>

        <h2 class="mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-cyan-400 bg-clip-text text-4xl font-extrabold text-transparent md:text-5xl">
          星界AI：你的创意无限引擎
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300">
          星界AI，集多种 AI
          模型于一体，为你的创意提供无限可能。立即体验，开启你的无限创作之旅！
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Items -->
      <div class="grid gap-20">
        <!-- 1st item -->
        <div class="items-center md:grid md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-6">
          <!-- Image -->
          <div
            class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-xl md:order-1 md:col-span-5 md:mb-0 md:w-full md:max-w-none lg:col-span-6"
            data-aos="fade-up"
          >
            <img
              class="mx-auto h-auto max-w-full rounded-xl md:max-w-none"
              src={FeatImage01.src}
              width="540"
              height="405"
              alt="Features 01"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Content -->
          <div
            class="mx-auto max-w-xl md:col-span-7 md:w-full md:max-w-none lg:col-span-6"
            data-aos="fade-right"
          >
            <div class="md:pr-4 lg:pr-12 xl:pr-16">
              <div class="mb-4 inline-flex rounded-full bg-cyan-400/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-semibold text-cyan-400">
                More AIs. Less spend
              </div>
              <h3 class="mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-cyan-300 bg-clip-text text-3xl font-bold text-transparent">
                AI 文本生成：解放你的文字创作
              </h3>
              <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-gray-300">
                无论是小说、诗歌、剧本、论文，还是邮件、文案、代码，星界AI集成了Gemini、Claude、ChatGLM、LLama等全网顶级
                AI
                语言大模型，为您提供流畅自然的文本生成，助您轻松应对各种写作需求。
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-4">
                {
                  [
                    '第一时间更新全网最先进的AI模型',
                    '内置专业prompt应用，自定义专属GPTs',
                    '一键切换模型，实时召唤全网AI为您服务',
                  ].map((item) => (
                    <li class="flex items-center">
                      <div class="mr-4 flex size-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500/20 to-cyan-400/20">
                        <svg
                          class="size-4 fill-current text-cyan-400"
                          viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        >
                          <path d="M10.28 2.28L3.989 8.575 1.695 6.28A1 1 0 00.28 7.695l3 3a1 1 0 001.414 0l7-7A1 1 0 0010.28 2.28z" />
                        </svg>
                      </div>
                      <span class="text-gray-300">{item}</span>
                    </li>
                  ))
                }
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 2nd item -->
        <div class="items-center md:grid md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-6">
          <!-- Image -->
          <div
            class="rtl mx-auto mb-8 max-w-xl md:col-span-5 md:mb-0 md:w-full md:max-w-none lg:col-span-6"
            data-aos="fade-up"
          >
            <img
              class="mx-auto h-auto max-w-full md:max-w-none"
              src={FeatImage02.src}
              width="540"
              height="405"
              alt="Features 02"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Content -->
          <div
            class="mx-auto max-w-xl md:col-span-7 md:w-full md:max-w-none lg:col-span-6"
            data-aos="fade-left"
          >
            <div class="md:pl-4 lg:pl-12 xl:pl-16">
              <div class="font-architects-daughter mb-2 text-xl text-purple-600">
                More AIs. Less spend
              </div>
              <h3 class="h3 mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-200">
                AI 图片生成：点燃你的视觉灵感
              </h3>
              <p class="mb-4 text-xl text-gray-300">
                星界AI整合了Midjourney、DALL-E、Stable
                Diffusion等强大的文生图AI模型，只需输入简单的文字描述，就能生成精美绝伦的图片，满足你对各种风格和主题的视觉需求。
              </p>
              <ul class="-mb-2 text-lg text-gray-300">
                <li class="mb-2 flex items-center">
                  <svg
                    class="mr-2 size-3 shrink-0 fill-current text-green-500"
                    viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  >
                    <path d="M10.28 2.28L3.989 8.575 1.695 6.28A1 1 0 00.28 7.695l3 3a1 1 0 001.414 0l7-7A1 1 0 0010.28 2.28z" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>根据文字描述生成图片</span>
                </li>
                <li class="mb-2 flex items-center">
                  <svg
                    class="mr-2 size-3 shrink-0 fill-current text-green-500"
                    viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  >
                    <path d="M10.28 2.28L3.989 8.575 1.695 6.28A1 1 0 00.28 7.695l3 3a1 1 0 001.414 0l7-7A1 1 0 0010.28 2.28z" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>满足各种风格和主题的视觉需求</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg
                    class="mr-2 size-3 shrink-0 fill-current text-green-500"
                    viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  >
                    <path d="M10.28 2.28L3.989 8.575 1.695 6.28A1 1 0 00.28 7.695l3 3a1 1 0 001.414 0l7-7A1 1 0 0010.28 2.28z" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>提供专业的设计平台界面</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 3rd item -->
        <div class="items-center md:grid md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-6">
          <!-- Image -->
          <div
            class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-xl md:order-1 md:col-span-5 md:mb-0 md:w-full md:max-w-none lg:col-span-6"
            data-aos="fade-up"
          >
            <img
              class="mx-auto h-auto max-w-full md:max-w-none"
              src={FeatImage03.src}
              width="540"
              height="405"
              alt="Features 03"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Content -->
          <div
            class="mx-auto max-w-xl md:col-span-7 md:w-full md:max-w-none lg:col-span-6"
            data-aos="fade-right"
          >
            <div class="md:pr-4 lg:pr-12 xl:pr-16">
              <div class="font-architects-daughter mb-2 text-xl text-purple-600">
                More AIs. Less spend
              </div>
              <h3 class="h3 mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-200">
                AI 音乐生成：谱写你的旋律梦境
              </h3>
              <p class="mb-4 text-xl text-gray-300">
                星界AI集成了Suno等AI音乐生成模型，可以根据你的描述和风格偏好，创作出独一无二的音乐作品，让你轻松拥有专属的背景音乐或歌曲。
              </p>
              <ul class="-mb-2 text-lg text-gray-300">
                <li class="mb-2 flex items-center">
                  <svg
                    class="mr-2 size-3 shrink-0 fill-current text-green-500"
                    viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  >
                    <path d="M10.28 2.28L3.989 8.575 1.695 6.28A1 1 0 00.28 7.695l3 3a1 1 0 001.414 0l7-7A1 1 0 0010.28 2.28z" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>根据创作主题自动生成歌词及风格</span>
                </li>
                <li class="mb-2 flex items-center">
                  <svg
                    class="mr-2 size-3 shrink-0 fill-current text-green-500"
                    viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  >
                    <path d="M10.28 2.28L3.989 8.575 1.695 6.28A1 1 0 00.28 7.695l3 3a1 1 0 001.414 0l7-7A1 1 0 0010.28 2.28z" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>根据歌词自动选择风格并生成音乐</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center">
                  <svg
                    class="mr-2 size-3 shrink-0 fill-current text-green-500"
                    viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  >
                    <path d="M10.28 2.28L3.989 8.575 1.695 6.28A1 1 0 00.28 7.695l3 3a1 1 0 001.414 0l7-7A1 1 0 0010.28 2.28z" />
                  </svg>
                  <span>轻松拥有专属的定制音乐或歌曲</span>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 4th item -->
        <div class="items-center md:grid md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-6">
          <!-- Image -->
          <div
            class="rtl mx-auto mb-8 max-w-xl md:col-span-5 md:mb-0 md:w-full md:max-w-none lg:col-span-6"
            data-aos="fade-up"
          >
            <img
              class="mx-auto h-auto max-w-full md:max-w-none"
              src={FeatImage04.src}
              width="540"
              height="405"
              alt="Features 04"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Content -->
          <div
            class="mx-auto max-w-xl md:col-span-7 md:w-full md:max-w-none lg:col-span-6"
            data-aos="fade-left"
          >
            <div class="md:pl-4 lg:pl-12 xl:pl-16">
              <div class="font-architects-daughter mb-2 text-xl text-purple-600">
                More AIs. Less spend
              </div>
              <h3 class="h3 mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-200">
                AI 思维导图：激发你的无限创意
              </h3>
              <p class="mb-4 text-xl text-gray-300">
                星界AI提供AI思维导图功能，帮助你整理思路，发散思维，激发灵感，让你的创意转化为清晰的思维框架。
              </p>
              <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6">
                <div class="-mb-2 text-lg text-gray-300">
                  <li class="mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <svg
                      class="mr-2 size-3 shrink-0 fill-current text-green-500"
                      viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    >
                      <path d="M10.28 2.28L3.989 8.575 1.695 6.28A1 1 0 00.28 7.695l3 3a1 1 0 001.414 0l7-7A1 1 0 0010.28 2.28z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>根据主题词自动发散概念的思维导图</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="mb-2 flex items-center">
                    <svg
                      class="mr-2 size-3 shrink-0 fill-current text-green-500"
                      viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    >
                      <path d="M10.28 2.28L3.989 8.575 1.695 6.28A1 1 0 00.28 7.695l3 3a1 1 0 001.414 0l7-7A1 1 0 0010.28 2.28z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>整理思路，发散思维</span>
                  </li>
                  <li class="flex items-center">
                    <svg
                      class="mr-2 size-3 shrink-0 fill-current text-green-500"
                      viewBox="0 0 12 12"
                      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    >
                      <path d="M10.28 2.28L3.989 8.575 1.695 6.28A1 1 0 00.28 7.695l3 3a1 1 0 001.414 0l7-7A1 1 0 0010.28 2.28z" />
                    </svg>
                    <span>激发灵感，转化创意</span>
                  </li>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>